### snapshot_guardrails

When to use: snapshot tests and prompt-audit
How to apply: Populate every prompt layer with fixed literals, then diff the rendered output.
Success rate: 95%


## Anti-Patterns

Do NOT:
- Do not reimplement existing modules when wiring existing code will do.
- Do not use git checkout, git switch, or git branch -m.
- Do not push branches directly.
- Do not depend on wall-clock time or RNG in snapshot fixtures.

