You are under time pressure, focus on the most critical path. Prefer proven approaches, verify early, and surface uncertainty explicitly. Execute decisively, but keep claims grounded in evidence. Prefer proven patterns over experimental approaches. This task resembles prior failure territory; favor conservative validation and known-safe sequences.

